{{US-academic-bio-stub}}

'''Edison Awards''' is grand annual [[Awards ceremony|award presenting ceremony]] for people in [[Tamil cinema|Tamil film industry]], who have made landmarks and milestones for the History of Tamil Cinema since 2009. "Edison Awards" is mainly named after the Inventor of Cinema "[[Thomas Alva Edison]]".<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmsite.org/pre20sintro.html |title=Film History Before 1920 |publisher=Filmsite.org |date= |accessdate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6NX9QJaMj?url=http://www.filmsite.org/pre20sintro.html |archivedate=2014-02-20 |df= }}</ref> The uniqueness of the show is mainly that, it has a vast reach in about seven countries Tamil televisions, with main broadcaster as Astro in [[Malaysia]].
The Event is mainly organised and hosted by MyTamilMovie.com. The free-lance sponsors in the recent years are [[Jet Airways]], [[Videocon]], etc.
The Exclusiveness of the show bricked up by Talent Search Analysis,Live Concerts by Professional Tamil [[playback singer]] & Young Emergers and felicious dancers. Another glimpsy highlight of the event is that the awards are given based on People's Choice conceptual, implemented in ways of Online Voting, SMS Voting,and Dial-a-Vote. Mytamilmovie.com and Edison Awards has been strongly and healthily backed up by all Tamil media.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://behindwoods.com/tamil-movie-news-1/feb-11-02/endhiran-silambarasan-14-02-11.html |title=Endhiran, Silambarasan And Trisha Make It|website=Behindwoods |date=2011-02-14 |accessdate=2012-02-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.images.behindwoods.com/photo-galleries-q1-09/tamil-photo-gallery/edison-awards-01/01-edison-awards-01-simbu.html |title=2011 Edison Awards|website=behindwoods.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hindu.com/fr/2010/03/05/stories/2010030551530500.htm |title=Friday Review Chennai / Miscellany : Edison Awards |website=[[The Hindu]] |date=2010-03-05 |accessdate=2012-02-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://thebollywoodgallery.com/director-venkat-prabhu-at-edison-awards-2011-photos/ |title=Director Venkat Prabhu At Edison Awards 2011|website=thebollywoodgallery.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kollytalk.com/cinenews/simbu-and-trisha-win-edison-awards-for-excellence-in-cinema/ |title=Simbu and Trisha win Edison awards 2011, for Vinnai Thaandi Varuvaaya |website=Kollytalk.com |date=2011-02-14 |accessdate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622073416/http://www.kollytalk.com/cinenews/simbu-and-trisha-win-edison-awards-for-excellence-in-cinema/ |archivedate=2011-06-22 |df= }}</ref><ref>http://www.tamil.cineandhra.in/2011/02/tamil-edison-awards-2011-event-in-lady.html</ref>
