'''Gabriele Levy''' (born 9 October 1958) is an Italian sculptor, writer, [[web master]].
Levy's work is entirely dedicated to the letters of the [[hebrew alphabet]], which are made in various materials.<ref>G. Di Matteo "Mondi Ebraici", ''Agenfax'' 13 June 2011 http://www.agenfax.it/cultura-e-spettacolo/mondi-ebraici_20430.html</ref><ref>Maria Valabrega. "Uno sguardo sulla cultura ebraica" La stampa, 9 March 2010 [http://www.lastampa.it/_web/cmstp/tmplrubriche/torinosette/grubrica.asp?ID_blog=132&ID_articolo=877&ID_sezione=294&sezione=]</ref>
